Firms in the US sell dog and cat biscuits containing cannabidiol, or CBD, taken from hemp . 
  Compounds in the plant have been known to alleviate joint pains, treat mood disorders and help pets lose weight . 
  Canna Companion uses hemp from the Cannabis sativa strain in its capsules and biscuits . 
  Hemp is used legally in a range of ways and is legal in many countries . 
 